{"tid":534123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港列「全球十大不快樂地區」　施永青：子女太早過豐裕生活，不易快樂","createTime":"2018-01-19T13:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T15:43:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"633b87b16bbfc1f34c61588127a21960d2f00e5a","tid":534123,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180118/s00001/55cc973fb69775dba7860ba9a2928931.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180118%2Fs00001%2F55cc973fb69775dba7860ba9a2928931.jpg&h=d9577cb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國民調中心蓋洛普調查發現，香港於「全球十大不快樂國家或地區」中排名第七。中原地產主席施永青表示，一個人是否快樂受主觀心理狀態影響，認為「父母若是讓子女太早可以過豐裕的生活，只會令他們將來不容易感到快樂」。<br />\n<br />\n施永青於《am730》專欄表示，一個人是否感到快樂，未必與客觀條件直接有關，「更多的是受主觀的心理狀態所影響」。他說香港老一代大都比新一代快樂，是因為他們經歷過比今天更艱苦日子，又提到中國人有謂「難得少年窮」、「窮過的人應比富過的人更容易快樂」，故父母若是讓子女太早可以過豐裕生活，只會令他們將來不容易感到快樂。<br />\n<br />\n施永青之後提到，曾遇過一名關心社會的年輕人，抱着一腔熱誠想獻身社會，卻因眼見佔中無所獲、公民抗命難以改變北京收緊對港政策現實，故感到愈來愈無奈，開始意興闌珊。<br />\n<br />\n施永青認為，這名年輕人感到苦悶，因為他什麼都要求完美，總想一步登天，而不理會客觀環境是否容許：「他們怎可以只有一套終極方案，而不肯作任何妥協？而且還要求香港人都得跟隨他們的標準。那就不只會害苦自己，還把香港人也拖了下水，變得沒法快樂起來。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180118/s00001/1516267006866\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180118%2Fs00001%2F1516267006866&d=n%2BuvdDj2NgJc0J2E9Am1PKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=c95458fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180118%2Fs00001%2F1516267006866&h=b651939d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180118/s00001/1516267006866</a>"},{"pid":"85049188917d3a40bd9a664caddf5e37c7f81aae","tid":534123,"uid":59898,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:20:23.000Z","msg":"屌你老母聖誕快樂呀施狗"},{"pid":"3e68e5d50c25e10498e8b2ca867532d339477a47","tid":534123,"uid":20058,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:20:39.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲老屎忽思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c7acf0f7e39160bc631933d2789aaa2877071e","tid":534123,"uid":71994,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:22:43.000Z","msg":"呢係老屎忽真係用屎忽嚟諗嘢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9243e1dd5bec5c90d2a72438149753476ad99aec","tid":534123,"uid":126046,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:23:30.000Z","msg":"香港一日仲有依啲仆街係度 <br />\n仲用佢果個年代啲思維諗野同做野<br />\n我諗譜羅大眾都真係好難快樂囉"},{"pid":"8a06a929a28801837443ac4104eaa30a1ea1237b","tid":534123,"uid":78620,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:25:53.000Z","msg":"如果有一日施永青死, 應該會令到全港年輕人快樂指數暴力拉升"},{"pid":"9682a7ed10d780e0aeb1586cbd47caf84e3a36ca","tid":534123,"uid":42735,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:27:30.000Z","msg":"細個要將人地送比佢既聖誕卡改名送比人最快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03aeea5f8417cfe9d513d0d4e9a89b1f8847a7a","tid":534123,"uid":129453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個要將人地送比佢既聖誕卡改名送比人最快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n垃圾"},{"pid":"bfe264b691a0b522732e7182bfa0de8f86fd3e92","tid":534123,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:26:29.000Z","msg":"今日後生唔苦就唔會成日有學生跳樓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6763a936733af1d7e11f2b3ebea284af53aad3b","tid":534123,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:33:17.000Z","msg":"後生仔食下屎先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb2e6a733e29e32391ca0986a8cf6c5d711b768","tid":534123,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":0,